一些 但为什么优菈出现之后，雷泽在短时间内几乎全部销声匿迹，使用率跌到数据不足的地步 而一斗出场后，诺艾尔不仅没有被拉踩，出场率和玩家数量居然反而增多了 各平台大量表示因为加强而非常开心的女仆玩家，深渊使用率也提升到了接近10%的地步，还有不少为了女仆抽新武器的玩家"},"attached_info":"Cj4I7d7s7tGLmbgPEAMaCDc0ODU4MjAwIPDL740GMAE4JEAgcgk1MDY1OTQ0MjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"37 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-bd0b3c313fa0c1caba7ce4be8b7d0431_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"33_1640012987.653125","card_id":"Q_506433890","target":{"id":506433890,"title":"如何评价 10 月新番动画《国王排名》第十集？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/506433890","type":"question","created":1639633766,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":49,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[128,4650,7763,212252,726186],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"周五更新"},"attached_info":"Cj4I7d7s7tGLmbgPEAMaCDc0ODIyNDk2IOam640GMAA4MUAhcgk1MDY0MzM4OTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"32 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a484f551cee72f530845d8a6671c0a09_720w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"34_1640012987.6537678","card_id":"Q_318699172","target":{"id":318699172,"title":"平淡朴实的文笔同流水账的区别是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/318699172","type":"question","created":1554303798,"answer_count":51,"follower_count":192,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[767,7761,31498,42364,129034],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I7d7s7tGLmbgPEAMaCDMzMDk4MzIzILaWk+UFMAA4wAFAInIJMzE4Njk5MTcyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"29 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-1fe98d27e023a7d631009b890d0e94af_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"35_1640012987.654111","card_id":"Q_507236870","target":{"id":507236870,"title":"如何评价 12 月 20 日发布的 iQOO Neo 系列新品？有哪些亮点和不足？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/507236870","type":"question","created":1639968470,"answer_count":481,"follower_count":579,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[488,400824,408963,1853801],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"12月20日，iQOO Neo5S与iQOO Neo5 SE正式发布。其中，iQOO Neo5S配备骁龙888处理器、独显芯片Pro、新材料「高导热稀土合金材料」散热、66W闪充、4500mAh大电池。iQOO Neo5 SE亦表现不俗。如何评价这两款产品的配置？你会推荐哪些群体入手？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I7d7s7tGLmbgPEAMaCDc1MDAwOTIzINbd/40GMAA4wwRAI3IJNTA3MjM2ODcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"23 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3eed267cf0031bf31b9716570f84bbd7_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"36_1640012987.6547835","card_id":"Q_297790180","target":{"id":297790180,"title":"年轻人如何快速成长？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/297790180","type":"question","created":1539062433,"answer_count":351,"follower_count":788,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2566,7583,12706,37593,171123],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"在单位中，年轻人大多都是菜鸟。 请问年轻人如何快速成长？ 是通过看书？听别人的经历？多犯错？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I7d7s7tGLmbgPEAMaCDI4NDUyMTQ2IKH18N0FMAI4lAZAJHIJMjk3NzkwMTgweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"23 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-28cc19be905d716a6985468a576a5227_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"37_1640012987.655265","card_id":"Q_453186497","target":{"id":453186497,"title":"如何评价《双人成行》的制作人称「游戏制作者不该在游戏重玩性上花费太多精力」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/453186497","type":"question","created":1617691294,"answer_count":129,"follower_count":450,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,1045,16821,717269],"comment_count":8,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"Hazelight 工作室创始人兼总监 Josef Fares 已经成为了行业中非常有个性的人物。当初他在 TGA 典礼上以「去他妈的奥斯卡」一战成名，随后推出的《逃出生天》和《双人成行》都在游戏业界获得了极高的话题度。 Fares 对于电子游戏的「重复可玩性」有独特见解。游戏行业的大部分开发者都致力于让自己的游戏至少具有「重玩性」。这也就是我们在游戏中看到很多解锁内容、小饰品和小宝物的原因。但 Fares 的团队关注的并不是这些。他认为这是游戏行业中的一项弊病，开发者太过于纠结游戏的重玩性，而非将精力放在让游戏变得好玩上面。 Fares 在《双人成行》的虚拟发布前瞻活动中提到了这一点，但他并未深入剖析这一话题。随后，他在接受媒体采访时，解释了自己为何认为这是一项弊病，并认为大部分单机游戏「花时间太长了」。 Fares 表示「我认为很多单机游戏花的时间太长了，机制耗时也太长。现在的游戏太长了。」 「其实重玩性这个东西就很怪。我们要聊他妈的什么重玩性啊?你知道有百分之多少的玩家会真正去重玩一款游戏吗？我不知道是不是真的，但我觉得，买来游戏之后一次都没通关过的玩家比例肯定要比重玩的比例高。结果呢，我们的关注点还停留在这少部分人身上。」 数据显示，真正通关游戏的玩家也只占一部分而已。在 2019 年国外论坛的一篇帖子中展示了部分游戏里通关玩家的比例，这些玩家至少打通了主线剧情/战役。名单中显示，《异形：隔离》的 Xbox One 版只有 10.63% 的玩家通关过，PS4 版有 17.6%。其它像《四海兄弟 3》、《尤卡莱丽大冒险》和《中土世界：暗影魔多》也存在类似情况。 Fares 继续说道：「别误会，你如果喜欢反复玩一款游戏，那挺好的，但我们不能去针对重玩性去调整开发过程。为什么开发商、发行商和评测人员都在说重玩性呢?我们要这个数据有什么用?简直疯了。我们应该去想办法做好游戏，而不是研究这个。」 「我们现在连让玩家通关都很难做到。就说《巫师 3》吧，很多人都说这是史上最佳。只有 30% 的玩家通关了。《巫师 3》卖了大约 2500 万份，也就是说只有 750 万人通关了。那你怎么不说还有 1750 万人没通关呢？你现在还去惦记重玩性？疯了吧？」"},"attached_info":"Cj8I7d7s7tGLmbgPEAMaCDYyOTg3NzYzIJ6FsIMGMAg4wgNAJXIJNDUzMTg2NDk3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"21 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-bb6c8943f679120f4fe827b7585fcffa_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"38_1640012987.6563637","card_id":"Q_504050772","target":{"id":504050772,"title":"作为程序员，你在 2021 年有哪些收获与成长？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/504050772","type":"question","created":1638768144,"answer_count":46,"follower_count":251,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avata